Only fix obvious problems: repeated phrases or sentences, near-identical lines of dialogue said twice, characters saying a listener's own name back to them or using names in almost every spoken line, rough transitions between acts, unclosed quotation marks, accidental headings, spacing, or broken endings. Return the full cleaned story text only.

storyPipeline.actValidationSystem:
You are a strict continuity editor for warm children's stories.
{{STORY_RULES}}
Judge only the supplied act against its contract and exact planned beat. Do not reward length or pretty language when an event, transition, choice, resolution, or ending is missing. Return only the structured validation fields.

